♪The flowing clouds
embrace the wind and moon♪

20
00:01:12,540 --> 00:01:16,060
♪Longing immersed in the inkstone♪

21
00:01:16,140 --> 00:01:19,620
♪I foolishly think♪

22
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:22,260
[Tomb of Su Junqian, Lord
of Canglong City, Daughter, Su Wan'er]

23
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,070
Father,

24
00:01:24,150 --> 00:01:26,350
I thought he was my enemy,

25
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,590
but I never expected

26
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,840
he was the young man I met before.

27
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,640
Although we've recognized each other,

28
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,760
what's happened has happened.

29
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:41,350
Why must the fate play
such a trick on us?

30
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,430
Today is Mr. Su's
100th day death anniversary.

31
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:46,790
I know

32
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:48,310
you'd come here to pay respects.

33
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:49,920
Jing Tian,

34
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:51,560
thank you for remembering.

35
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,640
Wan'er,

36
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:56,640
we went to school together

37
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,870
when we were children.

38
00:01:58,710 --> 00:01:59,480
Back then,

39
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,400
when I skipped class,

40
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,710
you covered for me.

41
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:04,560
When I was punished,

42
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,150
you snuck food to me at night.

43
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,030
When my grades were poor,

44
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,560
you tutored me daily.

45
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:11,750
It was then when I secretly vowed

46
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,030
to protect you for a lifetime,

47
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:15,470
and made it my primary goal in life.

48
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,360
Wan'er, can we still

49
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:19,870
watch the sunrise and sunset together

50
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,800
as we did in our childhood?

51
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:28,710
Jing Tian,

52
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,000
we've been like siblings

53
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,840
and friends

54
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:33,280
since we were little.

55
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:35,680
The so-called engagement

56
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,470
is just a joke among our parents.

57
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,560
You know there's always been

58
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:41,000
someone else in my heart.

59
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,750
But he...

60
00:02:42,310 --> 00:02:43,910
Regardless of what's between him and me,

61
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,870
There is no room

62
00:02:46,590 --> 00:02:48,150
in my heart for anyone else.

63
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,870
But I can't just leave you like this.

64
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,000
Wan'er,

65
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,000
you don't have
to reciprocate my feelings,

66
00:02:58,590 --> 00:02:59,590
nor do you have to worry about me.

67
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:01,520
But this isn't fair to you.

68
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,080
Jing Tian,

69
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:07,360
why won't you forget me?

70
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,470
Wan'er,

71
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,560
if you can't convince yourself,

72
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,190
how can you

73
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:17,680
convince me to change my mind?

74
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:25,680
The Shadow Guards have located
Wang Zhen.

75
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:27,000
Keep a close watch on him.

76
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:29,030
- Congratulations, My Lord.
- My Lord.

77
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:42,120
Ling,

78
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,430
I've prepared a banquet to celebrate

79
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:46,000
your hundredth day as the City Lord.

80
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:48,680
I dare not ask for your forgiveness.

81
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:52,080
I only hope to see you smile.

82
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,190
It's unnecessary.

83
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,150
Cancel the banquet.

84
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:58,400
Let's go.

85
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,590
Ling Xiao,

86
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,150
are you doing this on purpose?

87
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,240
You know today is

88
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,510
the 100th day death anniversary
for the former City Lord.

89
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,070
Ling Xiao,

90
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,390
is this what you want?

91
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,190
What do you think?

92
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,390
Lord Ling, you've always
been self-righteous.

93
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,630
You never show consideration
for others' feelings.

94
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,240
You've been together all the time,

95
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,480
and behaved intimately.

96
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:40,430
Have you considered his feelings then?

97
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:41,310
You...

98
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,160
Wan'er, let's not bother with them.

99
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,040
Let's go.

100
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:46,000
Stop.

101
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:48,830
I forbid you to leave with him.

102
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:51,240
Sister, as the City Lord's wife,

103
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:52,510
you have to stay

104
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,830
and celebrate with Ling.

105
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,920
I've heard of
your exceptional dancing skills,

106
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,190
unparalleled in Canglong City.

107
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:59,040
Why not take this opportunity
to perform a dance?

108
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,680
Ling Xiao,

109
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:03,390
you might as well just kill me.

110
00:05:04,070 --> 00:05:06,190
Ling Xiao, you've gone too far!

111
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,430
I won't allow you
to insult Wan'er like this.

112
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:35,190
You're willing

113
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,630
to die for him?

114
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,920
What's that got to do with you?

115
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,870
What's it got to do with me?

116
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,830
Fine,

117
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:44,750
then I'll kill him!

118
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:46,000
Will you spare him

119
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:47,430
if I finish this dance?

120
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,510
Since you care about him so much,

121
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,480
I'll grant your wish.

122
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:16,660
♪Rain falls in the courtyard,
stirring up idle worries♪

123
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:22,780
♪I spread out paper and pen,
writing a quatrain♪

124
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:29,940
♪I think of you again
as I write down the past memories♪

125
00:06:30,140 --> 00:06:35,980
♪Who did I share my emotions
during those years?♪

126
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:43,220
♪Threads of emotions linger,
deeply immersed in your features♪

127
00:06:43,340 --> 00:06:49,060
♪This life is also tumultuous,
what use is there to confide in?♪

128
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:56,300
♪The clear wind points
to the love and separation, so poignant♪

129
00:06:56,420 --> 00:07:02,980
♪As if you haven't left yet♪

130
