♪This life is also tumultuous,
what use is there to confide in?♪

141
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:18,940
♪The clear wind points
to the love and separation, so poignant♪

142
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,160
Ling Xiao, let her go!

143
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:37,540
♪People sit silently by candlelight
as night begins♪

144
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:43,460
♪A play of sorrows and joys,
your role, my outline♪

145
00:08:43,580 --> 00:08:48,740
♪Though the dream is over,
the feelings are hard to let go♪

146
00:08:48,780 --> 00:08:50,420
♪Everyone is filled with
sorrow and pity♪

147
00:08:50,540 --> 00:08:54,300
♪Alas, the mortal world
has too many spectators♪

148
00:08:55,700 --> 00:09:01,420
♪You turn back to ascend
the stage wearing a green robe♪

149
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:07,380
♪A song asking about heart matters,
but who will answer?♪

150
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:13,140
♪An old dream with infatuation
and resentment and complications♪

151
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,620
♪You sing for me♪

152
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:18,580
♪In the play,
telling of separations and reunions♪

153
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:24,540
♪Pear blossoms fall
and flowing sleeves feel like yesterday♪

154
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:30,700
♪The heart is closed,
unable to gaze the emotional eyes♪

155
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:33,620
♪This life is filled
with too much affection♪

156
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:37,420
♪Amid the applause,
who can see through it?♪

157
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:42,820
♪Aren't the characters
in the play you and me?♪

158
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:10,320
My Lord.

159
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:40,030
Ling, what are you...

160
00:10:45,390 --> 00:10:46,200
Niyue,

161
00:10:46,630 --> 00:10:48,600
how long are you going
to keep lying to me?

162
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:24,940
♪The weathered years,
the yellow old marks♪

163
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:31,100
♪Memories of a lifetime
in the past dreams♪

164
00:11:31,180 --> 00:11:36,900
♪The residual snow, the shining stars,
the hazy midnight moon♪

165
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:42,380
♪Strong liquor cannot dispel
the melancholy of love♪

166
00:11:42,900 --> 00:11:48,540
♪The green mountains form a line
and the river reflects the moon♪

167
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:54,140
♪Time flies like an arrow,
what day is today?♪

168
00:11:54,500 --> 00:12:00,580
♪Spring returns with warmth again,
and birds are everywhere♪

169
00:12:00,780 --> 00:12:05,660
♪This love only awaits
your reciprocation♪

170
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:11,780
♪Who will hold my hand now?
Your beautiful smile can make me drunk♪

171
